  # VERTICAL BRIDGES - UPWARD TO VOID (4 bridges, 3 nodes each)
  # Connect horizontal synergy_1 nodes to void synergy nodes (tier 5 ↔ tier 5)
  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  # FIRE_SYNERGY_1 ↔ VOID_SYNERGY_1
